data.description: LOCATION AND OPPORTUNITY!! Possibilities are endless with this remodel in the heart of downtown Stanwood.  Gorgeous updates and upgrades. Amazing in-home business potential, income-generating investment rentals, live-in and rent-out partially, or MIL unit. This property really is a show stopper with open concept great room, a dining area showcasing built-in buffet-style storage & a Massive chef's kitchen for entertaining. Even a spacious utility room. Updates include NEW flooring, new trim, new fixtures new windows New electrical panel, New sinks and cabinets etc. Newer roof too!  This property has unlimited potential and options. Walk to local shops & restaurants. Close to schools, parks & water activities. 52'X75' parking lot in back
